							<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 text-slate-400 text-sm space-y-2 print:text-slate-700">
								<li>Built canonical integration hub for DHL, DPD, and RoyalMail shipping providers.</li>
								<li>Implemented custom caching and decision logic (Drools) for international commerce.</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white print:text-black">Technical Consultant</h3>
								<span class="text-sm text-slate-500">2011 – 2013</span>
							</div>
							<p class="text-accent font-bold mb-3 print:text-blue-600">Daon India | Client: UIDAI (Aadhaar)</p>
							<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-4 text-slate-400 text-sm space-y-2 print:text-slate-700">
